I"f<p>Welcome to Quantum Field Theory I</p>

<p>The prerequisites are as follows:</p>
<ol>
  <li>A strong background in high school mathematics, including trigonometry, solving algebraic equations, working with exponentials and logarithms, and graphing.</li>
  <li>An exposure to physics is useful; many examples will be drawn from physics.</li>
</ol>

